metadata.title: Piper PA-28 Cherokee
aws::graph::propositions: # Current Production Variants of Piper PA-28 Cherokee (2022)
Piper PA-28 Cherokee is an aircraft.
Five variants of the PA-28 are in production as of 2022.
Archer TX is a variant of the Piper PA-28 Cherokee.
Archer LX is a variant of the Piper PA-28 Cherokee.
Archer TX has a 180 hp (134 kW) Lycoming IO-360-A4M engine.
Archer LX has a 180 hp (134 kW) Lycoming IO-360-A4M engine.
Archer TX has a 128 kn (237 km/h) TAS maximum cruise speed.
Archer LX has a 128 kn (237 km/h) TAS maximum cruise speed.
Archer TX has a 522 nmi (967 km) range.
Archer LX has a 522 nmi (967 km) range.
Archer TX has a Garmin G1000 avionics suite.
Archer LX has a Garmin G1000 avionics suite.

text:
As of 2022, five variants of the PA-28 are in production:

Archer TX and LX with a 180 hp (134 kW) Lycoming IO-360-A4M engine, a 128 kn (237 km/h) TAS maximum cruise speed, 522 nmi (967 km) range and a Garmin G1000 avionics suite
Archer DX and DLX with a 155 hp (116 kW) Continental CD-155 engine, a 123 kn (228 km/h) TAS maximum cruise speed, 848 nmi (1,570 km) range and a Garmin G1000 avionics suite
Pilot 100i with a 180 hp (134 kW) Lycoming IO-360-B4A engine, a 128 kn (237 km/h) TAS maximum cruise speed, 522 nmi (967 km) range and Garmin G3X avionics.
